# Faz 11: Performance + Load Test

## Goal

Lighthouse CI PR gate (performance ≥80, accessibility ≥90, best practices ≥90). Initial bundle <200 KB gzipped; strategic route splitting. DB hot path `EXPLAIN ANALYZE` + index fixes. k6 scenarios: login storm (100 concurrent), case list (1000 req/min), transition burst, dashboard — P95 <500 ms @100 concurrent, 0 critical error rate.

Detay: `Docs/10_IMPLEMENTATION_ROADMAP.md` §Faz 11.

**Bağımlılık:** Faz 0–10 feature-complete; staging deploy green. Scale assumption: `Docs/00` yıllık 200–250 bildirim, düşük/orta eşzamanlılık.

