### Files NOT touched

- Feature functionality changes (perf-only diffs)
- Production IaC — Faz 13

## Constraints

### Use

- Measure before optimize — bottleneck-driven fixes
- Lighthouse CI blocking thresholds
- Strategic lazy routes — critical path stays sync
- k6 P95/P99 from histogram — not average only
- Index changes via Prisma migration

### Avoid

- Premature React.memo everywhere
- Critical path dynamic import
- Optimize without measurement
- Ignore a11y for perf wins

## Done Definition

### CI & Frontend

- [ ] Lighthouse CI PR gate active
- [ ] performance ≥80, accessibility ≥90, best-practices ≥90
- [ ] Initial bundle <200 KB gzipped

### Database

- [ ] Hot path EXPLAIN ANALYZE documented
- [ ] Index migration applied staging

### Load Test

- [ ] k6 P95 <500 ms @100 concurrent
- [ ] 0 critical error rate
- [ ] P95/P99 histogram reviewed (not average-only)

### Human Gate

- [ ] Bottleneck report attached to PR
- [ ] PR squash merge → `main`

### Manual smoke test

```bash
pnpm --filter @ethics/web build && pnpm analyze  # bundle report
pnpm lighthouse:ci  # or CI job re-run
k6 run infra/k6/case-list.js --env STAGING_URL=...
```

## Explicit Don'ts

- Premature optimization
- Critical path lazy load regression
- k6 average-only metrics
- Feature changes disguised as perf
- Skip histogram review
- `main`'e direct push

